{"tid":2019444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.28上環衝突 落完口供即銷毀現場記錄 高級督察：非官方文件有權自行處理","createTime":"2020-05-16T09:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T13:41:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88b03618f041b056b71ce5581ac9d6fdf6ac3c7d","tid":2019444,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）去年7月28日上環爆發警民衝突，新婚夫婦湯偉雄和杜依蘭、及17歲李姓少女被控暴動罪，今早於區域法院續審。辯方今日開始盤問，當日小隊指揮官承認，小隊曾有「傳令員」作現場記錄，他並依賴該「幾張紙」落口供，惟該記錄用完後「就掉咗」，亦無作影印，因為並非官方文件，「毋需有任何人指示或訓示或命令就可以作出銷毀」。旁聽人士聽罷嘩然。當辯方問及催淚彈的詳情時，控方一度提出反對，指催淚煙的影響和使用屬不公開資料，不應廣泛予外界知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073471&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=fe7df72c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073471&h=4ef6cad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073471</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f7266c72c2008ec1d7e3c693bb0a48ad7ea96c","tid":2019444,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c25fc29e755f0edc3c1369dbd61a46f2a30b75","tid":2019444,"uid":95138,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ffe0c2d0b39845a40bfe0dcbfcc29a34772010","tid":2019444,"uid":165749,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-1